<p>Internet Minimum Advertised Price (IMAP) Terms &amp; Condition Policy and Sales Rules &amp; Regulations</p>
<p>for the Toprankon.com Line of Products (effective 7/20/2017)</p>
<p>__________________________________________________________________________________________________</p>
<p>As a condition of being a Wholesaler of Toprankon.com products, adherence to the following terms and conditions is required. Failure to abide by these terms and conditions will result in your being discontinued as an authorized Wholesaler of any and all Toprankon.com products.</p>
<p><strong>IMAP Policy</strong></p>
<p>An Internet Minimum Advertised Price (&ldquo;IMAP&rdquo;) policy has been established for all Toprankon.com products. The IMAP policy applies to all online locations for these products and all internet and like electronic media.  &ldquo;Online location&rdquo; is defined as the virtual place where Toprankon.com products can be purchased by end-users. The IMAP applies to all advertisements for Safer Medical of MT Inc. products in any and all virtual/online media including, but not limited to, virtual/online: websites, shopping carts, newspapers, magazines, catalogs, flyers, coupons, mailers (including eBlasts, etc.), email, and like electronic media. A wholesaler may NOT sell ANY Toprankon.com products on Amazon, eBay, Walmart, Jet, etc.</p>
<p><strong>IMAP Policy Violations</strong></p>
<p>Wholesaler understands that a violation of this policy is immediate grounds for terminating the relationship with Toprankon.com  Wholesaler will be notified of all violations and instructed to cease and desist all sales that are in violation of the IMAP policy.</p>
<p><strong>Disclosure of all Company Names</strong></p>
<p>Wholesaler acknowledges full disclosure of all of its corporate names and business names under its controls (DBA&rsquo;s – Doing Business As) to Toprankon.com and has disclosed a list of any such business names to Toprankon.com</p>
<p>Wholesaler understands that multiple accounts under different business names but under the control of a parent corporation or owner with Toprankon.com are not permitted.  All orders with Toprankon.com shall occur from the parent corporation or business.</p>
<p><strong>Promotions or Changes to MSRP and IMAP Policy</strong></p>
<p>The manufacturer may periodically reformulate Toprankon.com products or engage in promotions with respect to certain items.  In such cases, IMAP prices may be suspended or modified with respect to these products by timely notifying all Wholesalers of such change.  Such notification shall be made in writing to the Wholesaler by fax, email, or letter.</p>
<p>The manufacturer retains the right to modify MSRP at any time and will notify Wholesalers of such price modifications. All Wholesalers must implement such modifications within thirty (30) days from the date of receipt of such notice.</p>
<p>The IMAP may be adjusted by Toprankon.com (the manufacturer) at its sole discretion upon seven (7) day notice to you by letter, email, or fax.  Such adjustments shall be uniformly applied to all Wholesalers.</p>
<p><strong>Privacy Policy</strong><br>
  As a user of our website you can be confident that we will:</p>
<p>Only collect information required for fulfilling the services requested.<br>
  Never share personal info with anyone and/or organization unless required to do so by law authorities.<br>
  Give you access to your information and remove your information from our system on your request.<br>
  Use all the appropriate security technology to keep your information and our website safe.<br>
  This policy was last updated on June 16th, 2017. Please review this page often as this policy could be subject to change.</p>
<p><strong>WHAT WE COLLECT</strong><br>
  You are in no way obliged to give personal information to Toprankon.com, but please understand that refusing to do so will affect your use of our website.</p>
<p><strong>PURCHASES</strong><br>
  In order to purchase a product(s) from Toprankon.com one will be required to provide the following :</p>
<p>Full Name<br>
  Mailing  Address<br>
  contact Number<br>
  E-mail Address<br>
  Credit Card Info</p>
<p>We only request this information as it is necessary to complete all sales transaction. Please be advised that we take every reasonable precaution to keep your information safe and secure.</p>
<p><strong>SURVEYS</strong><br>
  At Toprankon.com we periodically conduct customer surveys. You must understand that the decision to submit information to Toprankon.com in this manner is completely yours, and by doing so you are forfeiting any rights to said information, and therefore such information will legally become the property of Toprankon.com This information will be used internally and will not be disclosed to the public or to any third party in a way that will identify you as the author of the information.</p>
<p><strong>CUSTOMER TESTIMONIALS</strong><br>
  All information submitted to TheHairRock in the form of a customer testimonial will become the property of Toprankon.com We can choose to display such information in any way we deem appropriate. In the event your customer testimonial is put on public display, the testimonial may include your name, age, as well as the city and state/province in which you live (Example: Great Job! Jane Doe, San Diego, California).</p>
<p><strong>EMAIL NEWSLETTERS</strong><br>
  Toprankon.com issues an e-mail newsletter containing account and wordpress related tips, new product launches, etc.</p>
<p><strong>ANALYTICS</strong><br>
  Toprankon.com uses analytic methods (tracking pixels and JavaScript) as a way to monitor the performance of the website. Through this process, we collect anonymous information about how users interact with our website. This information is used internally in order to help us improve the Toprankon.com user experience.</p>
<p><strong>COOKIES</strong><br>
  The functionality of this website depends on the use of browser cookies. A browser cookie is a small file (roughly 4kb) that allows our server to identify your computer.</p>
<p>You must enable cookies to complete a purchase from our site. If you have your browser set to not accept cookies, please be advised that the website will not function properly.</p>
<p><strong>HOW WE PROTECT YOU</strong><br>
  We ensure that:</p>
<p>Our employees and associates are held accountable for any information they have access to.<br>
  We limit the collection of information to that which is relevant to our cause and purpose.<br>
  We will not disclose your information to a third party without your consent unless required to do so by law.<br>
  All your personal information is kept at a secure location.<br>
  We use all appropriate security software to ensure your information is kept out of harm&rsquo;s way.<br>
  We use 128-bit SSL (secure socket layer) encryption on all pages that transmit personal information from your computer to our server.</p>
<p><strong>COLLECTING INFORMATION FROM MINORS</strong><br>
  Anyone under the age of 18 is allowed to browse our website, however, they are forbidden from making purchases or participating in any other service that involves the collection of personal information. This policy is designed to protect the privacy of children.</p>
<p><strong>LINKS TO OTHER WEBSITES</strong><br>
  A link does not imply an endorsement of a website. Although Toprankon.com may link to another website, it does not mean we have control or share responsibility for the content and security of that website.</p>
<p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please <a href="https://Toprankon.com/contact-us/">contact us.</a></p>
<p>Thank you, and we hope you enjoy shopping at Toprankon.com.</p>
